{
  "stem": "449.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, but when I came back from Egypt, I had-- I had some savings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the guy-- an electrician in-- in-- in-- in Egypt-- he-- he was an Italian, and he had no money.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He would go bankrupt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he asked me, could you lend me money?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A young fellow, I was stupid again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A great part of my savings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Never saw it again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, yeah, the-- then-- then I went-- then I went to Turkey.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was only short time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was maybe six-- six months that-- then I stayed in-- in Modling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] that was now four years I was in the-- in Egypt.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I come back, I saw a-- a new kid, very lonely.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so-- but somehow I found out it was a Jewish-- Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was very lonely-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] there was a Purim ball.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't have-- I never could dance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I sent her an invitation to the Purim ball, but I didn't go there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was-- I was not out for a-- for a girl.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I saw only a lonely kid, always walking the same-- she went shopping for the family-- always the same.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I saw it, and I said, she has to join us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She has to-- to be with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I sent her a-- [LAUGHS] it didn't go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Disappointing-- she went there, and she was still alone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then I had a dog, and she had a dog, and these dogs just started to get acquainted, so we got acquainted.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That's how I met her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And after a while, yeah, and then I-- I left Turkey-- I left for Turkey and told her that we should get together.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
